comments: VanVleet (TOR) makes contact to Mills' (SAS) arm that affects his ability to gather the ball.
DeRozan (SAS) gathers the ball on his left foot and then takes two steps prior to releasing the ball on the shot attempt.
Lowry's (TOR) arm makes contact with the ball during DeRozan's (SAS) driving shot attempt.
Gay (SAS) places two hands on Siakam (TOR) during the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Murray (SAS) makes contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it from VanVleet (TOR).

Mills (SAS) moves laterally and he does not establish a legal guarding position in Siakam's (TOR) path when the contact occurs. Siakam gathers the ball with two hands prior to the contact and this play should be assessed as a shooting foul.
Anunoby (TOR) jumps vertically with both arms in a legal position as he absorbs the oncoming contact with Murray (SAS) during his driving shot attempt.
DeRozan (SAS) and Boucher (TOR) mutually engage in marginal contact prior to disengaging during the loose ball.
Boucher (TOR) commits a take foul on Gay (SAS).
Mills (SAS) makes contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it from Siakam (TOR) during the drive.
Following the rebound, Lowry (TOR) makes contact with Johnson (SAS) that affects his FOM.
